node.text: Extra Creamy Cheesecake? Yes, plz!!! This classic recipe is rich, decadent, and so satisfying! And it can be fully prepared up to 5 days in advance! Just keep it covered in the fridge! Need to make it even further in advance? It freezes great for up to 2 months! Just remember to thaw in the fridge the night before you plan on serving! https://bakerbynature.com/extra-rich-and-creamy-cheesecake/
